periences occur and which give Augustine a three-fold access to God.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aChristian saintszAlgeriazHippo (Extinct city)vBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aChristian saintszAlgeriazHippo (Extinct city)xBiographyxHistory and criticism. 0aSpiritualityxChristianityxHistoryyEarly church, ca. 30-600. 0aSpiritualityxHistoryyEarly church, ca. 30-600. 4aHistory : Medieval Studies. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Theology. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / Catholic.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791484999423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791484999/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles